file=AI & Agents/README.md · a&a:AI & Agents Department=**8 agents** — Fleet governance, rapid prototyping, integration & security, model benchmarking, quality monitoring, continuous improvement, ecosystem scanning, and edge technology adoption.\n · tb=\| Agent \| Role \| · tb=\|-------\|------\| · tb=\| **meta** \| Fleet governance & standards — agent architecture, fleet registry, skill authoring \| · tb=\| **proto** \| Rapid prototyping — prototype kit, eval-first design, promote-or-archive \| · tb=\| **relay** \| Integrations & security — MCP tool registry, integration patterns, egress allowlists \| · tb=\| **forge** \| Model/technique benchmarking — degradation diagnosis, technique adoption \| · tb=\| **gauge** \| Fleet quality monitoring — agent scorecards, fleet health reports \| · tb=\| **anneal** \| Continuous improvement — self-annealing loop, skill lifecycle \| · tb=\| **scout** \| Ecosystem scanning — marketplace skill scouting, tool evaluation \| · tb=\| **edge** \| Cutting-edge tech adoption — landscape assessment, pilot specs \| · a&a:AI & Agents Department=**Department doc:** [DEPARTMENT-WORKFLOW.md](DEPARTMENT-WORKFLOW.md)\n